node.text:
It was a joy to meet UNHCR Goodwill Ambassador and fellow Olympian @YusraMardini and hear her incredible story, from fleeing Syria all the way to her second Olympics with the @refugeeolympicteam!
See you at #Tokyo2020! @refugees
#StrongerTogether

node.text: In honor of #HungerActionMonth this September, join me in raising gallons to help our communities get milk to those in need. node.text:
As the final countdown begins to the Olympic and Paralympic Games, I am proud to partner with @PoloRalphLauren as a #RLxTeamUSA athlete.

Designed in red, white, and blue, #PoloRalphLauren unveils our Team USA Opening ceremony uniform featuring official USA patches and the iconic Polo Pony.

Follow along here on the road to Tokyo and learn more about how #PoloRalphLauren supports Team USA. 

#TeamUSA
